Verizon Communications Inc And Motorola Solutions Announce To Deliver Vertical Enterprise Solutions With Wireless Data And Voice
Monday, 20 Feb 2012 08:45am EST
Verizon Communications Inc and Motorola Solutions announced that the two companies will leverage each other's expertise to help grow machine-to-machine (M2M) connections, and deliver vertical enterprise solutions with wireless data and voice. Verizon Enterprise Solutions will offer end-to-end integrated voice and data solutions, while Motorola Solutions' product portfolio will allow enterprise and government IT organizations to capitalize, capture and analyze critical data. Critical elements to that equation include device staging, vertical applications, rollout support and help desk services.Â 
